Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.49,0:00:06.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走起來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.75,0:00:08.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我天生就是打仗的料\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I was born for battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.83,0:00:11.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,具備打仗應有的素質\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Built for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.92,0:00:17.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有時在戰斗中 精心設計的計劃會遭破壞\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sometimes in battle, a perfectly crafted plan gets compromised.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.26,0:00:22.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一位真正的將軍 當場就能想出一個更好的計劃\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A true general comes up with a better one right there on the spot,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.51,0:00:25.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冒著風險采取行動\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}working without a net
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.18,0:00:31.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后在雷鳴般的掌聲中 圓滿地完成任務\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and sticking the landing to thunderous applause.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.07,0:00:37.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點 狗崽子們\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Hurry up, you dogs!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.82,0:00:39.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.70,0:00:47.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們在哪兒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Where are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.70,0:00:50.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們當時直沖我們過來 然后轉到了一條側軌上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- They were coming straight at us and then veered away on a sidetrack.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.71,0:00:51.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這條軌道拐向西南方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This line bends Southwest.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.00,0:00:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以那個速度 他們此刻可能已在20公里之外\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}At that speed, they could be 20 kilometers away by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.59,0:00:56.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者已調頭 跟在我們后面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Or coming about to nip at our heels.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.25,0:00:57.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 先生 這事事先沒一點征兆\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I'm sorry, sir. There was no warning.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.84,0:01:01.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然 他們確保了這一點 不是嗎  趁沒有衛星信號\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- No, they saw to that, didn't they? No satellite coverage.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.30,0:01:03.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在無月之夜 從陰影中伏擊我們\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A moonless night. An ambush from the shadows!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.76,0:01:05.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就跟他們離開的那天一樣懦弱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- As cowardly as the day they left, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.64,0:01:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 他們從我們身邊經過肯定有陰謀\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- No, they didn't drive by for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.52,0:01:10.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把前燈開到最大\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Forward lamps to full.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.19,0:01:14.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎車\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Brake!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.69,0:01:21.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在戰斗中 有那么一刻 你被對方的第一擊擊中后\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's a moment in a fight when that first blow lands
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.32,0:01:22.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切仿佛都靜止了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and everything stops.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.74,0:01:27.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那一瞬間 你心開目明 認清了自己是誰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And in that flash of clarity, you know who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.66,0:01:33.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會竭盡全力奪回我的機車\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll push as hard as it takes to get my engine back.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.92,0:01:38.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1023節車廂長的雪國列車\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Snowpiercer, 1,023 cars long.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.69,0:01:58.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加大馬力 沖過去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Full thrust. Push through it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.11,0:02:01.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-可是 先生 如果車軸… -全速前進 工程師 快\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Sir, if that axel-- - Full power, Engineer. Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.29,0:02:12.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得漂亮 先生 第一局您贏了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Well done, sir. Round one to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.62,0:02:16.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 他們放那個陷阱 不是為了讓我們停下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- No, no, that trap wasn't meant to stop us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.13,0:02:17.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是為了讓我們減速\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It was meant to slow us down.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.67,0:02:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱文 我們今天不能受任何挫折\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We can't have any setbacks today, Kevin.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.59,0:02:22.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魯絲的人會受到激勵的 去把他們找出來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ruth's people will be energized. Find them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.21,0:02:23.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正好知道該從何著手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I know just where to start.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.67,0:02:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手段狠點\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Take the gloves off.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.80,0:02:27.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺雞儆猴\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Make an example.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.39,0:02:29.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就等著您這么吩咐呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I thought you'd never ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.77,0:02:33.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-凱文 還有件事 -您說 先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- And Kevin? - Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.23,0:02:36.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓扎拉到這里來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Send Zarah to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.61,0:02:40.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們現在的速度是多少\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What's our speed?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.19,0:02:41.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每小時14公里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- 14 kilometers an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.03,0:02:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊 雷頓先生 你已迫使我們慢如爬行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- All right, Mr. Layton, you got us at a crawl.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.32,0:02:47.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有什么花招呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What's the play?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.29,0:02:53.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷頓知道車尾對接是行不通的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Layton knows better than to connect end to end.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.70,0:02:56.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我手下的軍靴可以直接沖進去擊敗他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My Jackboots would just sweep in and crush him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.04,0:03:00.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 他會從側面襲擊我們\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So he's going to peck at us from the side.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.29,0:03:01.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他需要一條并行的軌道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- He needs parallel track.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.46,0:03:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而這片鐵路站場就像個迷宮 布滿了并行軌道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- And this rail yard is an entire maze of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.81,0:03:23.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們擺脫了陷阱 但速度慢了下來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He broke free of the snare but slowed down.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.98,0:03:26.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們可以在這些側線上 趕上他們 與其并行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- We can get right up alongside him in these sidings.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.61,0:03:28.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們距離那里還有2公里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They'll be in position in 2 kilometers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.91,0:03:30.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本 調頭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Bring us around, Ben.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.16,0:03:31.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-收到 -有多少時間\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Copy that. - How long we got?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.33,0:03:32.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三四分鐘\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Three, four minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.24,0:03:33.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 機警點 咱們把這事給辦了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- All right, stay sharp. Let's get this done.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.08,0:03:35.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去確保喬西已做好準備\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll make sure Josie's ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.75,0:03:39.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貝絲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Bess.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.88,0:03:43.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貝絲提爾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}♪ Bess Till
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.59,0:03:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-貝絲  -奧德麗 閉嘴\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}♪ Bess! - Audrey, shut it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.38,0:03:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出什么事了 是他嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- What's happening? Is it him?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.76,0:03:52.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的腦袋被插在長矛上時 你就會知道是他了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You'll know it's him when his head is on a pike.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.27,0:04:01.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你準備好了嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You ready for this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.48,0:04:05.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本開到他們邊上后 我就跳過去 進大愛麗絲的機車\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Ben takes us close. I jump over, breach the Big Alice engine,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.32,0:04:06.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后你們重新連接兩車\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and you reconnect.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.19,0:04:08.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們只有一次機會\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- We only get one shot at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.32,0:04:11.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就最好別錯失這個機會\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Well, then, better not miss it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.93,0:04:38.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扎拉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Zarah,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.89,0:04:40.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你來得正是時候\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}just in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.89,0:04:42.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得你該看看這個\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thought you should be here for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.56,0:04:44.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以人質的身份還是旁觀者的身份\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- As a hostage or a spectator?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.44,0:04:46.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以我的紅顏知己的身份\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- As my confidante, nothing less.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.82,0:04:47.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.40,0:04:49.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.20,0:04:53.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看一下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Have a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.99,0:04:55.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到沒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}See,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.37,0:04:59.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從我們側翼悄悄追上來的 是你的舊相好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that's your old life creeping up our flank.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.16,0:05:01.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們要攻擊我們嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Are they attacking?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.50,0:05:04.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許他們是來投降的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Maybe they're here to surrender.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.00,0:05:06.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看到白旗了嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You see any white flags?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.42,0:05:11.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-沒有 -沒有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- No. - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.05,0:05:13.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果非得讓我猜的話\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, and if I had to guess,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.22,0:05:15.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得他們是沖著龍首而來的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'd say they're trying to cut the head off the snake.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.76,0:05:18.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我有個驚喜要送給他們\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I have a surprise for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.93,0:05:22.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（W 壓縮氧）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.36,0:05:27.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳下去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Heave.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.90,0:05:31.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點傳\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Heave.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.20,0:05:35.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管這些錫罐是做什么用的 肯定不是什么好事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Well, whatever these tin cans are for can't be good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.49,0:05:37.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,派克 你有什么計劃\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Pike, man, what's the plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.91,0:05:42.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,專心干活\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Keep your eyes on your work.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.16,0:05:44.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-繼續傳 -嘿 別呆站著\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Heave. - And quit standing around! Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.04,0:05:47.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點 你在干什么呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Come on. What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.00,0:05:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 該行動了 我去引開他們 你們去找魯絲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- All right, time to move. I'll distract them. You guys get to Ruth.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.88,0:05:54.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 不能這么做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- No. Whoa, whoa. That's not how it works, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.59,0:05:56.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你現在是負責人了 你不能被抓\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're in charge now. You don't get caught.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.02,0:06:05.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接著\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Catch.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.79,0:06:27.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們已經就位\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- We're in position.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.21,0:06:30.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（冷封門已鎖）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.38,0:06:31.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（冷封門解鎖）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.55,0:06:33.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喬西 是時候了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Josie, it's time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.26,0:06:35.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在外面當心點\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Be careful out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.13,0:06:37.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會毀掉那引擎的 別擔心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I'll breach the bastard, don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.77,0:06:44.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是現在 魚叉炮\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now! Harpoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.02,0:06:46.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備發射\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Deploy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.15,0:06:52.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在打開冷封門\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Opening cold-lock.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.50,0:07:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,威爾福德有一個 像大炮的玩意兒 往后撤\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wilford has a cannon or something. Pull back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.58,0:07:07.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上更換軌道 喬西 抓緊了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Switch track. Josie, hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.46,0:07:10.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（軌道切換）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.39,0:07:21.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我們要脫軌了 -設法穩住\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- We're derailing! - Try to stabilize.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.81,0:07:23.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得漂亮\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.48,0:07:29.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你總能令我驚訝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Never fails to amaze me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.19,0:07:32.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受到這么大刺激 卻沒什么反應\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You take so much in and give so little back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.36,0:07:36.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我剛射殘了你男人的列車 扎拉 可你連眼睛都沒眨一下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I just hobbled your man, Zarah, and you didn't even flinch.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.62,0:07:43.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照這個速度下去 黎明前這場戰爭就會結束\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}At this rate, the war will be over by daybreak.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.13,0:07:59.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托 嘿 這節車廂受損 我們得離開這里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Come on. The car is damaged. We gotta go. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.55,0:08:03.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得把車廂斷開 否則我們會脫軌的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- We have to cut it loose. It's gonna derail us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.14,0:08:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從這里斷開 那可是四節車廂啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Cut here? That's four cars.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.68,0:08:06.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是最近的連接處 這是唯一的選擇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- It's the closest J-link. It's the only option.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.06,0:08:08.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-阿莎在那后面 -我們沒時間了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Asha's back there. - We don't have time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.48,0:08:11.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.81,0:08:12.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.90,0:08:13.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.82,0:08:16.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在外頭堅持了八年 不能上我們列車第二天就被害死呀\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- She waited eight years outside. Can't very well kill her on day two.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.69,0:08:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安全栓已解除\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Safety's off.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.87,0:08:24.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始斷開連接\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Disconnecting now
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.04,0:08:25.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（連接處解鎖）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.29,0:08:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斷開了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And we're clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.30,0:08:38.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.35,0:08:44.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在這里會更安全\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You'll be safer up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.60,0:08:49.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.60,0:08:52.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不會有事吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You gonna be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.69,0:08:58.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把燈關了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Turn out the lights.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.82,0:09:01.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.99,0:09:06.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待著別動 好嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hold fast, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.04,0:09:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們有麻煩了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- We have a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.20,0:09:52.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,威爾福德不見了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wilford's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.04,0:09:56.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他關閉了列車的信號和燈光 不知道他們在哪里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}His train went dark. He could be anywhere now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.17,0:10:05.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關閉全車上下的通訊和信號傳輸 停止一切聲響\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Switch off comms and transmitters tip to tail. Not a peep.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.60,0:10:13.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扎拉 你怎么還站著呀\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Zarah, what are you doing still on your feet?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.48,0:10:15.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定累壞了 過來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You must be exhausted. Come.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.15,0:10:20.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你有什么打算\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- So what are you planning?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.57,0:10:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微歇一下對我們有好處\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Bit of a lull. It'll do us good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.78,0:10:31.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喘口氣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Catch our breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.37,0:10:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在你和這孩子身上投入了很多\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've invested a lot in you. And the child.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.67,0:10:38.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想讓你待在我身邊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I just want to keep you near me,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.96,0:10:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了保護你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}for your protection.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.13,0:10:43.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且如果我在機車里 他們就不會攻擊這里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- And because they won't attack the engine if I'm in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.72,0:10:45.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.40,0:11:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十幾公里長的列車 你怎么能跟丟了呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- How do you lose a 10-mile train?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.49,0:11:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我們把他帶到這片迷宮里的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- We were the ones that led him into this maze.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.99,0:11:08.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他可能想逃出去 這六條線路通向谷外\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- He could be running. These six routes head out of the valley.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.57,0:11:10.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果他進入了直線軌道 我們就失去了優勢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If he gets to linear track, we'll lose our advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.62,0:11:13.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 他也可能 正在下一個拐角等著我們\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Yeah, or he's around the next corner, laying in wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.20,0:11:15.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他會把我們的列車一節節地廢掉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- He's gonna pick us off piece by piece.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.46,0:11:17.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時那玩意的炮口正對著我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I looked into the muzzle of that thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.12,0:11:19.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們必須找到他 我們能去高一點的地方嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- We need to get eyes on him. Can we get to higher ground?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.71,0:11:23.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這里 這條軌道沿著山脊線 應該能讓我們看到整個盆地\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Here, track follows the ridgeline. Should give us a view of the whole basin.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.17,0:11:26.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 就這么辦 把燈熄了 如果他打算隱身 我們也一樣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Okay, let's do it. Lights out. If he's gonna go dark, so do we.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.23,0:11:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小情侶 起來干活了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Up and at 'em, lovebirds.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.98,0:11:42.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱文 出去 你太過分了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Kevin! Get out. How dare you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.40,0:11:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夜車被我征用了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Commandeering the Nightcar.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.98,0:11:45.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱文\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Ugh, Kevin.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.15,0:11:46.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰批準的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- On whose authority?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.32,0:11:48.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以稱之為“戰時舉措”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Call it a wartime measure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.86,0:11:51.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們沒聽說嗎 雷頓回來了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, you didn't hear? Layton's back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.66,0:11:53.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.24,0:11:55.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有活兒要干呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's work to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.64,0:12:18.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不你去煮點咖啡吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Why don't you, um, go put some coffee on?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.66,0:12:31.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰在那里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Who--who's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.45,0:12:35.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是來見囚犯的 我是她的律師\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Here to see the prisoner. I'm her lawyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.08,0:12:38.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得現在已經沒有律師這回事了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I don't think that's a thing anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.96,0:12:41.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,軍靴 你把頭盔摘掉了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Lose your helmet, Jackboot?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.08,0:12:42.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 別這樣 哥們\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Hey, come on, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.75,0:12:43.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.25,0:12:45.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你認識我嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Do you know me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.46,0:12:50.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是個末等人 抱歉 我不知道你叫什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You're--you're a Tailie. Forgive me, I-I don't know your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.18,0:12:52.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認識你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I know you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.47,0:12:54.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你姓惠金斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Whiggins.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.26,0:12:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.72,0:12:59.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關于末等人 有兩件事你該知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Well, there's two things you should know about Tailies.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.98,0:13:02.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的記性很好 而且打仗我們總贏\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We have long memories and we win wars.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.56,0:13:04.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Oh, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.07,0:13:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上一場戰爭是我們贏了 這一場也一樣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We won the last one. And we'll win this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.49,0:13:12.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想當個礙我們事的人嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And do you wanna be the guy who stands in the way?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.12,0:13:15.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惠金斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hmm, Whiggins?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.24,0:13:20.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,律師先生 給你十分鐘的時間\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You have ten minutes, Counselor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.75,0:13:23.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我替你開門\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let me just get the door for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.22,0:13:32.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,派克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Pike?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.13,0:13:34.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姑娘 你的氣色不錯啊 沒有缺胳膊少腿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You're looking good, girl, with those arms dangling down.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.59,0:13:36.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不該來這里 太危險了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You shouldn't be here. It's too dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.39,0:13:40.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我得把你弄出去 -等等 告訴我發生了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I'm gonna get you out of here. - Wait, wait, wait. Tell me what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.10,0:13:44.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,威爾福德用大炮把雷頓趕走了 此刻我們正在黑暗中瞎轉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Wilford drove Layton off with cannon fire. Now we're rolling around in the dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.94,0:13:48.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果威爾福德在躲著雷頓 那我們就得給雷頓發信號\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Well, if Wilford is hiding, then we need to signal Layton.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.32,0:13:51.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得先把你救出去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I'm gonna get you out of here first.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.44,0:13:55.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行的 要救我 你得先殺了惠金斯 然后找到克利福德\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You can't. You'd have to kill Whiggins, and then you'd have to find Clifford
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.32,0:13:57.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他也殺了 因為鑰匙在他手里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and kill him too, 'cause he's got the keys.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.83,0:13:58.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有誰 繼續說\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.95,0:14:02.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,派克先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Pike, Mr. Pike,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.91,0:14:05.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是個好人 一個勇敢的好人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you're a dear man and a brave one,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.04,0:14:07.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這場戰爭比你我都重要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but this war is bigger than us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.51,0:14:13.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要怎么給雷頓發信號呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- How do I signal Layton?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.14,0:14:17.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有個主意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I've got an idea,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.76,0:14:20.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你得去列車前列的待客部\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but you'll have to get uptrain to hospitality.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.98,0:14:33.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿莎 你還好嗎 在這里還行嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Asha. Hey, you good in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.36,0:14:37.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 我們讓你卷進了 最激烈的對抗中 來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry, I dropped you right in the thick of it. Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.95,0:14:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey, hey, hey, hey, hey, hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.78,0:14:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什么事了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.29,0:14:43.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,威爾福德先生把這列車弄壞了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did Mr. Wilford cripple the train?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.41,0:14:45.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有 聽著 這只是貓鼠之爭 好嗎 沒事的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- No, look, it's just some cat and mouse, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.96,0:14:47.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是貓\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.63,0:14:49.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們八個人 要對付偉大的威爾福德先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- And you're supposed to be the cat? Eight of you against the great Mr. Wilford.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.54,0:14:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“偉大的威爾福德先生” 跟你想象中的不一樣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- The great Mr. Wilford is not who you think he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.88,0:14:53.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是他救了你們大家嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Isn't he the one that saved all of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.67,0:14:55.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我們自己救了自己\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- We saved our own damn selves.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.26,0:14:57.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他打造這列列車 只是為了自己能稱王\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He built all of this just so he could be king.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.55,0:15:00.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-那現在輪到你稱王了 -不 這是我們的私人恩怨 好嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- So now it's your turn? - No. This is personal for us, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.81,0:15:03.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,登上列車時 我有一個伴侶 她現在懷著身孕\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have a partner that I boarded with. I have a child on the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.60,0:15:10.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你這么做是為了一個孩子 你會做出讓自己后悔的事的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Oh, if you're doing this for a child, you will do things that you will regret.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.11,0:15:13.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是過來警告你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I just came in to warn you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.15,0:15:15.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不會放棄的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We are not giving up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.90,0:15:18.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,局勢好轉之前 會變得更加惡劣 明白嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is gonna get worse before it gets better, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.74,0:15:20.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-明白 -堅持住\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Okay. - Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.63,0:15:33.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是我的陽光\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- ♪ You are my sunshine
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.46,0:15:37.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我唯一的陽光\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}♪ My only sunshine
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.43,0:15:41.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當天空灰暗時\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}♪ You make me happy
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.85,0:15:45.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會帶給我歡樂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}♪ When skies are gray
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.52,0:15:49.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你永遠都不知\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}♪ You'll never know, dear
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.40,0:15:53.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有多么愛你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}♪ How much I love you
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.61,0:16:00.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請別將我的陽光帶走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}♪ Please don't take My sunshine away
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.28,0:16:02.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要知道 你唱歌的時候\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You know, when you sing,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.45,0:16:06.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我幾乎都能說服自己說 你的為人并不壞\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can almost convince myself you're not a horrible person.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.12,0:16:07.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.75,0:16:12.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后我會想起來你只翻唱別人的歌 所以歌詞其實不代表你的心聲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- And then I remember you only sing covers, so the words aren't actually yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.63,0:16:15.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌詞只是點綴而已\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Lyrics are just dressing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.26,0:16:17.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只為他歌唱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I sing for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.38,0:16:19.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老天\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Oh, God.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.59,0:16:21.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你顯得很不屑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You scoff,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.64,0:16:25.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但歸根結底 那就是全部\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but at the end of the day, that's all there is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.77,0:16:27.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為之歌唱的那個人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A person you sing for.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.53,0:16:37.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貝絲 你的那個人是誰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who's that to you, Bess?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.66,0:16:47.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一路堅持到了世界末日 居然會沒有一個那樣的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How do you get all the way to the end of the world and have no one?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.29,0:16:50.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I have people.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.29,0:16:53.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.34,0:16:57.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷頓、扎拉、羅齊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Layton, Zarah, Roche.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.59,0:16:59.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅齊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Roche?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.51,0:17:00.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 羅齊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Yeah, Roche.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.93,0:17:04.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就像我的導師兼益友\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He was like a mentor to me and--and a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.97,0:17:09.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盡管我跟他對著干 他還是罩著我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Even though I fought him, he-- he had my back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.44,0:17:12.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我不會為他歌唱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, I don't-- I don't sing for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.61,0:17:15.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是每一天\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But not a day goes
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.69,0:17:18.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都在想著把他從抽屜房弄出來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}by when I don't think about getting him out of those Drawers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.82,0:17:21.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很遺憾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.74,0:17:26.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望他能活下來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I hope he survived.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.29,0:17:29.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呀\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.42,0:17:38.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們在山脊上了 注意觀察\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- We're at the ridge. Eyes up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.88,0:17:42.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果他在山谷里 這是能找到他的最佳位置\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If he is in the valley, this is the best vantage point.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.02,0:17:52.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-有發現嗎  -提爾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Anything? - Till?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.27,0:17:53.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有 什么都沒發現\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Negative. There's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.94,0:17:56.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他們不可能就這樣消失不見啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- But they can't just vanish.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.53,0:18:03.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（待客部）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.97,0:18:29.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（W 新年流程）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.06,0:18:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好戲登場\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Time to put on a show.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.09,0:19:02.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看南面 在山谷的盡頭 你們看到了嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To the south, far end of the valley. Are you guys seeing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.38,0:19:04.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的天啊 等等\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Oh, my God. Wait, wait, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.51,0:19:06.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is that-
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.18,0:19:09.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的支持者還在\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They're still with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.60,0:19:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到你了 約瑟夫\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- We see you, Joseph.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.63,0:19:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他正試圖逃跑 在山脊東側 往干線方向去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- He's making a break for it. East over the ridge to the trunk line.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.71,0:19:48.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他想偷偷溜出鐵路站場 我們在這里有戰術優勢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He wants to sneak out of the rail yard because it's where we have tactical advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.26,0:19:50.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他要是跑出去了 接下去好幾天就都是直線軌道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- If he gets out of the valley, he's looking at days of linear track.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.85,0:19:52.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們能趕到他前面去嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Can we beat him to it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.47,0:19:54.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-艾莉  -不行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Alex? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.93,0:19:56.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道 也許行吧 我沒把握\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't know, maybe. It's all assumptions.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.02,0:19:58.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們還等什么 加速啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- What are we waiting for? Pedal down.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.73,0:20:00.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們在山口截住他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Let's cut 'em off at the pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.73,0:20:04.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工程師 加足馬力\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Full throttle, Engineer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.23,0:20:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先生 恕我直言 我們的油耗非常快\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Sir, with respect, we're draining really fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.49,0:20:08.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微開慢點 燃油效率會更高\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A few ticks slower would be more efficient.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.32,0:20:09.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們已經看到我們了 他們要來了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- They've seen us. They're coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.74,0:20:15.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用上所有的儲備燃油 越過這該死的山脊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tap every last reserve and get us over that bloody ridge!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.55,0:20:28.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托 你這是干什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Come on! What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.93,0:20:33.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,強壯男孩 給你挑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- So you have a choice, Strong Boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.30,0:20:37.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來要我砸碎兩根手指呢 還是砸碎你的拇指\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can take two fingers next time or I can take your thumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.52,0:20:40.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也可以聰明一點\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Or you could be smart
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.56,0:20:43.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像你自告奮勇 到我桌子這里來時一樣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}like when you bravely volunteered to step up to my table here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.32,0:20:48.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,威爾福德只是要你提供信息 報出你同黨的姓名\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wilford just needs you to start talking and name your collaborators.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.78,0:20:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不干\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.66,0:20:55.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-不干  -拜托 別再折磨他了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- No? - Come on. Leave him alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.29,0:21:00.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-抓住他 -不要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Hold him. - Ah, no! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.30,0:21:08.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.59,0:21:14.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒答應過要趟這渾水\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I didn't sign up for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.26,0:21:16.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想經營夜總會 提供酒水和歌曲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just wanted to serve some drinks and play some tunes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.35,0:21:19.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能放松點嗎 戰爭都是丑陋的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Would you relax? War is not pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.64,0:21:21.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但威爾福德會獎勵我們的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But Wilford will reward us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.19,0:21:23.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前提是他能贏\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- If he wins.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.23,0:21:25.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他當然會贏\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Of course he'll win.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.73,0:21:28.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬一他輸了呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If he doesn't?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.11,0:21:30.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到時候雷頓進來發現這件事 知道我們也在場 怎么辦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- And Layton rolls in here, finds this? Finds us?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.99,0:21:33.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,威爾福德的傀儡夫妻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wilford's little wedding puppets.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.74,0:21:37.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行刑的人又不是我們 我們只是提供了場地而已\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- We're not the torturers, all right? We're just providing a venue.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.37,0:21:40.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得被肢解的這個家伙 可不會這么認為\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I'm sure the mutilated guy will be quick to sort that out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.25,0:21:44.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽著 如果你不打算開口\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look, if you're not gonna talk,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.38,0:21:47.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你就不再需要這舌頭了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I guess you don't need that tongue anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.21,0:21:48.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請抓好他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hold him, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.26,0:21:55.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓好他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hold him, hold him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.26,0:21:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,張嘴\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Open up.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.53,0:22:18.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽著 即便我們追上了他 我們還是要應付他的魚叉炮\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Look, even if we catch up with him, we still have the harpoon issue,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.41,0:22:19.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也沒法進行車尾對接\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and we can't connect end to end.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.87,0:22:22.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我們絕對打不過他的軍靴\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We'll never overpower his Jackboots.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.62,0:22:23.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- No.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.92,0:22:24.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- No.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.17,0:22:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我們得想辦法進入機車 我們需要引開他的注意力\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So we need a plan to get into his engine. We need a distraction.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.67,0:22:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧德麗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Audrey.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.89,0:22:45.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是要干什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.90,0:22:47.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手放在背后\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Hands behind your back.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.27,0:22:50.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手銬 我就知道你有性怪癖\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Ooh, handcuffs. I knew you had a kink.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.36,0:22:53.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Move.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.99,0:22:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝好運\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.41,0:23:06.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這里的氣氛很壓抑嘛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- It's moody in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.75,0:23:08.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Sit.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.26,0:23:14.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有多遠\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- How much further?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.26,0:23:18.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快到山脊了 但我們的燃油即將耗盡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- We're almost at the ridge, but we're basically running on fumes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.97,0:23:21.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續開 它能行的 然后就勝券在握了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Keep pushing. She'll make it. Then we're home free.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.27,0:23:27.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠著點 本\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Nice and easy, Ben.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.45,0:23:40.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約瑟夫\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Joseph.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.67,0:23:58.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大愛麗絲 這里是雪國列車 請回話\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Big Alice, this is Snowpiercer. Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.01,0:24:04.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪國列車呼叫大愛麗絲 請回話\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Snowpiercer to Big Alice, come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.93,0:24:06.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先生 我該回答嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Sir, should--should I answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.10,0:24:07.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.73,0:24:13.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大愛麗絲 請回答\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Come in, Big Alice.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.07,0:24:21.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這里是大愛麗絲 我在跟誰通話呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- This is Big Alice. To whom am I speaking?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.24,0:24:25.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,威爾福德 我是那個 擋在你和開放軌道之間的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I'm the guy standing between you and open track, Wilford.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.04,0:24:29.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看到了 這么說 現在就看誰的膽子更大了 是嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I see that. So it's a game of chicken, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.54,0:24:33.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按你們行進的速度 我覺得你開不到那么遠\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- At the rate you're going, I don't think you'll make it this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.50,0:24:36.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大愛麗絲的韌勁比你想象的強\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Oh, Big Alice has more fight than you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.88,0:24:39.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷頓 這次會面是你發起的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You called this meeting, Layton.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.47,0:24:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 有話快說 沒必要在這里做無聊的爭執\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So go on, or are we just gonna stand here pissing off our prows?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.39,0:24:49.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們離開時 你我有個約定\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- When we left, we made a deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.27,0:24:51.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我確保奧德麗安全…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I keep Audrey safe--
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.73,0:24:54.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得 我就不把大家殺了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I remember, and I don't murder everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.11,0:24:55.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我記得我們的約定\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, I remember the deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.61,0:24:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要提醒你一句 那是在脅迫下作出的約定\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It was made under duress, I'll remind you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.99,0:25:00.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我還是遵守了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I stuck to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.91,0:25:01.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扎拉呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Where's Zarah?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.03,0:25:06.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她就在這里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- She's right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.12,0:25:09.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滿面紅光\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Positively glowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.54,0:25:11.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在這里 安德烈 我沒事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I'm here, Andre. I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.88,0:25:13.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧德麗呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- And Audrey?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.29,0:25:16.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想聽到她的聲音\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I want to hear her.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.59,0:25:22.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得知道她沒事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I need to know she's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.30,0:25:28.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交出列車控制權 你就可以親自跟她說話了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Surrender the train and you can tell her yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.98,0:25:31.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交出控制權\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Surrender?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.94,0:25:35.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們會給你們一節頭等車廂 提供美食酒水\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- We'll give you a car in First, food, drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.19,0:25:38.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們倆可以相守到老\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You two can live out your years together.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.28,0:25:43.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說 我把一切都給你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- So I--I give you absolutely everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.12,0:25:46.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你只會給我一點小小的恩賜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and you give me a little piece back in return?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.62,0:25:48.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個提議太可笑了吧 雷頓\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's quite some offer, Layton.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.58,0:25:52.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的提議是 用非暴力的形式了結這件事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- The offer is, we end this without violence,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.54,0:25:57.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否則就回到那個鐵路站場 我們會把你拆成碎片\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}or you could roll back down into that rail yard and we'll pick you apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.92,0:25:59.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完了 先生 燃油耗盡了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- That's it, sir. We're tapped.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.43,0:26:04.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拒絕\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- No deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.36,0:26:27.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想聽聽她的聲音\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I...I want to hear her voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.84,0:26:42.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約瑟夫\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Joseph.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.61,0:27:02.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（危險）
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.03,0:27:06.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 本 我到冷封門了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- All right, Ben, I'm at the cold-Lock.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.46,0:27:21.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Soon, soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.89,0:27:34.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,設置自動駕駛 急速后退\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Auto-engaging hot reverse.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.56,0:27:36.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們應該調換一下車尾車頭 讓大愛麗絲在后面推\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We should switch helms and get Big Alice pushing again.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.94,0:27:38.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停車 工程師\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Full stop, Engineer.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.19,0:27:42.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關閉電源\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let her power down.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.03,0:27:44.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-什么  -約瑟夫\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- What? - Joseph.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.87,0:27:52.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不可能是好事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- That can't be good,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.79,0:27:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會是好事嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}can it?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.41,0:27:56.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- No.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.75,0:27:58.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪國列車\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Snowpiercer,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.83,0:28:01.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們沒動力 啟動不了了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we are dead on the tracks.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.67,0:28:05.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你們不跟我們連接 列車上所有的人都會凍死\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you don't reconnect, everyone will freeze to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.72,0:28:13.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這是不顧一切了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You're desperate.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.31,0:28:16.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你則沒得選擇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- And you have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.11,0:28:25.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備連接 哈維…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Prepare to connect. Javi, abre una cerveza, amigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.78,0:28:34.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指揮官 把你的突擊小組 派到連接點去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Commander, move your boarding party to the connection point.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.87,0:28:37.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發電不足容量\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Generation deficit.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.87,0:28:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整個列車的溫度正在下降\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Train-wide temperature is dropping right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.67,0:28:41.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最好把你的毛衣穿上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Better get your woolies on.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.88,0:28:44.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 小伙子們 準備好了嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- All right, boys, you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.46,0:28:49.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出去 瞄準中心點 記住射擊目標\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Move out. Remember where to aim.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.59,0:28:51.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們在準備連接了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- They're preparing to dock.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.60,0:28:54.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們別無選擇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- They've got no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.89,0:28:58.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又要開始了 快走 快\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's go, let's go. Move, move, move.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.52,0:29:00.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,駕駛艙沒問題\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Cap okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.19,0:29:05.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 留神點 進去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Hey, watch your back. Move it, move it!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.28,0:29:09.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這太瘋狂了 本\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- This is crazy, Ben.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.82,0:29:11.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呀 強盜生涯就是如此\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Yeah, pirate's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.74,0:29:13.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見鬼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.12,0:29:14.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You're all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.24,0:29:16.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用你敢開的最快速度倒車\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just reverse her in as fast as you dare.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.83,0:29:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見鬼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.79,0:29:22.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們就位之前不要與對方連接\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- And don't reconnect until we're in position.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.55,0:29:32.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 各位 記住 我們要先把對方清除干凈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Hey, remember, people, we're gonna clear it first.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.30,0:29:34.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武器準備好 上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Weapons ready? Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.06,0:29:46.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老天\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Christ.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.02,0:29:48.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喬瑟芬\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Josephine.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.40,0:29:50.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她回來了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She's back.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.61,0:29:53.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真夠有種的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The bloody balls.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.33,0:29:59.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是爬上來的嗎 小流浪漢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did you climb aboard, you little hobo?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.33,0:30:03.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這里有孕婦哦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Uh-uh, baby on board.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.17,0:30:07.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 你不會的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, you won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.46,0:30:09.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不會的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.05,0:30:17.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見鬼 真夠狠的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Damn. Good one.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.59,0:30:53.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫你的人退下 否則我就把你扔出列車去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Tell your men to stand down or I will throw you off this train.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.81,0:31:09.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是首席工程師威爾福德\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- This is Head Engineer Wilford.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.36,0:31:13.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突擊小組 退下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Boarding party, stand down.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.78,0:31:20.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不打算…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We will not be taking...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.95,0:31:24.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用武力拿下雪國列車\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Snowpiercer by force.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.33,0:31:31.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退下 放下武器\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Stand down. Weapons down.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.96,0:31:34.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的天啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.39,0:31:46.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下開心了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Happy now?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.40,0:31:49.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快說\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.99,0:32:05.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安德烈雷頓擁有了列車控制權\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Andre Layton has the train.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.04,0:32:10.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪國列車的公民們…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Citizens of Snowpiercer...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.09,0:32:19.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們回來了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're back.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.24,0:32:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,50米 40米\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}50 meters, 40 meters,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.79,0:32:50.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,25米\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}25 meters...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.55,0:33:03.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能就這樣結束了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- It can't be just over.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.72,0:33:11.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得該是選擇勝利一方的時候了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Well, I think it's about time we get on the right side of history.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.32,0:33:24.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.92,0:33:32.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oz,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.38,0:33:35.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我非常愛你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I love you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.57,0:33:58.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抵抗軍萬歲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Long live the Resistance!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.91,0:34:48.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-找到了 -魯絲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Ah, found it. - Ruth?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.70,0:34:51.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安德烈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Andre.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.66,0:34:55.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒穿制服 我都認不出你了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I never would have found you. You're in civvies.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.54,0:35:01.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得威爾福德 把他的好酒藏在這里了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I remembered that Wilford had a secret tipple up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.13,0:35:04.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我正需要喝兩口 沒錯 -我想著我們可以慶祝一下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Oh, could use some of that. - Wanna celebrate? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.63,0:35:08.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來 你能回來真是太好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Oh, welcome home. It's good to have you back.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.77,0:35:13.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道你能把大家團結在一起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I knew you'd hold everyone together.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.77,0:35:14.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得漂亮\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.02,0:35:18.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們來喝吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Let's do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.48,0:35:20.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他們放出來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Take them out.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.70,0:35:26.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他情況穩定\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- He's stable.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.70,0:35:35.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡莉情況穩定…還有安娜…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Carly's stable. And Anne--
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.26,0:36:31.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈維\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Javi.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.57,0:36:44.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.41,0:36:54.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Oh, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.58,0:37:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非洲之角這個暖點 你真的相信它能維持生命生長\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- This warm spot, the Horn of Africa, you really believe it can support life?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.38,0:37:10.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 魯絲 我們的未來就在那里 我非常堅信這一點\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Yeah, our future is there, Ruth. I believe it with all my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.01,0:37:15.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通往非洲之角的軌道是整個鐵路網內\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You know, the Horn of Africa, the approach is maybe the worst stretch of track on
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.06,0:37:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最糟的一段\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the entire network.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.18,0:37:19.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且氣候崩潰時 那里發生過一場戰爭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And there was a war there when the climate crashed.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.31,0:37:20.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我記得\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Yeah, yeah, I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.94,0:37:23.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都累壞了 安德烈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- The people are tired, Andre.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.23,0:37:25.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這六個月艱苦漫長 而你回來后的第一個命令\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's been a long six months, and your first order
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.36,0:37:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是要讓他們再經歷更多艱辛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}is gonna be to steer them right back into more hardship?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.48,0:37:29.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會下達命令 我們會投票決定\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Mm-mmm, there won't be an order. We'll put it to a vote.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.45,0:37:32.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-投票  -是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- A vote? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.91,0:37:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要讓大家看看 民主已經獲勝 我們要一起選擇前進的道路\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We'll show them that democracy has won. We'll choose our path forward together.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.95,0:37:40.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已經準備好面對投票結果了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- And you're prepared for the outcome of this vote?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.54,0:37:43.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會讓大家相信這值得冒險一試\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I am going to convince them that it is worth the risk.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.75,0:37:45.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪國列車已經損毀不堪 不拋錨已是萬幸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Snowpiercer's running on duct tape and prayers.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.96,0:37:48.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是一個真實的能下車的機會\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is a real opportunity to get off.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.51,0:37:52.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是對你的投票 安德烈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- It's also a vote on you, Andre.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.18,0:37:55.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,列車上的很多人并不支持你的領導\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Much of the train doesn't support your leadership.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.64,0:37:58.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件事不止關系到我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- This isn't just about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.35,0:38:01.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是梅蘭妮會想要的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's what Melanie would have wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.73,0:38:03.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.06,0:38:06.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去通知公證處\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll, uh, inform the notary.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.98,0:38:09.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道列車上的所有人 都會慎重地投出這一票\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know that everyone aboard will take their vote to heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.15,0:38:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但萬一投票結果是“不去” 你有這思想準備嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but are you prepared to accept it if they vote no?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.41,0:38:18.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你最好仔細琢磨一下要怎么說服大家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You better think long and hard about exactly what it is you're gonna tell them.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.71,0:38:30.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只準你待在三等車廂 而且禁止進夜車\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You're confined to Third and barred from the Nightcar.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.92,0:38:33.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-約瑟夫呢  -奧德麗 你站錯隊伍了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Where's Joseph? - You picked the wrong side, Audrey.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.05,0:38:39.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這該死的列車上有過正確的隊伍嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Has there ever been a right side on this goddamn train?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.02,0:38:44.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一切都會崩塌的 等著瞧吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's all gonna go to shit. You'll see.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.45,0:39:00.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直接扎穿了我的手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- It went straight through my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.66,0:39:03.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣你就能記住我們了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Something to remember us by.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.79,0:39:05.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看你呀\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Look at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.71,0:39:09.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪物來找它的創造者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A monster come for its creator.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.42,0:39:13.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有詩意吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's poetic, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.38,0:39:18.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷頓沒法把列車團結起來的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Layton can't hold it together, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.93,0:39:21.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們會再次拒絕他的領導\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They'll reject him again.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.93,0:39:25.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是這列車的靈魂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I am the train.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.28,0:39:40.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,投票\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- A vote?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.58,0:39:42.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.54,0:39:46.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你今天也會有投票的權利\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You'll get a vote today too.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.08,0:39:50.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,政治\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Politics.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.75,0:39:53.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當你是世上最后一個人的時候 就會忘記政治的存在\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You forget about them when you're the last person on Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.01,0:39:57.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.76,0:39:59.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先別忙著謝我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Don't thank me just yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.89,0:40:01.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有件事要你幫忙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's something I need to ask of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.56,0:40:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安德烈 你救了我的命\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You brought me back to life, Andre.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.77,0:40:09.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我幫什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.73,0:40:54.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位乘客同伴們\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- My fellow passengers...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.90,0:41:01.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是這列列車啟程以來第一次\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Today, for the first time since our departure...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.53,0:41:05.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由你們來決定我們的目的地\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you will have a say in our destination,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.58,0:41:09.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你們的選擇將決定我們的未來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and your choice will determine our future.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.75,0:41:13.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們已經知道 梅蘭妮犧牲了自己 為我們繪制了一份地圖\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}By now, you know that Melanie's sacrifice gave us a map.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.79,0:41:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,證明地球上有些地方正在變暖\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Proof that there are places on the Earth that are warming.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.30,0:41:22.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們之前輕裝出發 快速地測試了每一個暖點\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Traveling fast and light, we tested each of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.30,0:41:27.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘇拉威西島、古吉拉特邦、馬那瓜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sulawesi, Gujarat, Managua,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.60,0:41:29.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿塔卡馬\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the Atacama.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.06,0:41:32.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但它們都不合格\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And each one of these let us down.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.98,0:41:37.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道 當初我們分開列車的決定\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know that you have suffered badly
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.15,0:41:40.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害你們歷盡了艱苦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}because of our decision to break the train.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.49,0:41:45.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但還有一個地方 我覺得大家應該寄予希望\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But there is one more location on which I ask you to stake your hope:
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.83,0:41:48.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是非洲之角\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the Horn of Africa.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.62,0:41:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,返回那里的行程會充滿風險\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The journey to return there will be fraught with risk
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.08,0:41:53.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艱辛還將繼續\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and the hardships will continue,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.63,0:41:58.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這里有一個人 能讓我們重樹信心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but we have someone here who can renew our faith.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.22,0:42:04.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個我們以前覺得不可能存在的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Someone we had given up on believing in.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.14,0:42:14.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他這是在干什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- What's he doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.85,0:42:16.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會讓她自己跟你們說\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- But I'll let her tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.61,0:42:18.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在編瞎話\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- He's bullshitting.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.75,0:42:33.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫阿莎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- My name is Asha.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.42,0:42:37.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是一個幸存者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I am a survivor.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.09,0:42:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷頓在外面找到了我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Layton found me out there, outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.30,0:42:45.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在戶外 生長了樹木\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Along with trees,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.68,0:42:47.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青草\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}green grass...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.85,0:42:50.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和生命的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and life.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.64,0:42:55.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來自新伊甸園\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I come from New Eden.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.88,0:43:20.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是要你們 在我和威爾福德之間做出選擇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I'm not asking you to choose between me and Wilford.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.80,0:43:25.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是請你們在我們熟悉的列車\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I am asking you to choose between the train we know
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.14,0:43:28.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我們不熟悉的夢想之間做出選擇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and the dream we don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.60,0:43:34.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感謝大家作出的犧牲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you all so much for your sacrifices.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.52,0:43:44.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個故事需要一個英雄 所以我們就帶回了一個英雄\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The story needed a hero, and we brought one back.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.28,0:43:47.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鑒于那番表演\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Well, in the wake of that performance,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.95,0:43:49.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,投贊同票的人勝出\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the yeas have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.91,0:43:51.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幾乎是2比1的比例\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Almost two to one.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.54,0:43:54.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多說一個謊又怎樣呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- What's one more lie?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.66,0:43:57.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,區別在于 這是我們說的最后一個謊話\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- The difference is, this is the last one
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.46,0:43:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很懷疑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we will have to tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.29,0:44:01.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我開始覺得這列列車需要謊言\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Well, I doubt that. I've come to think this train demands a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.96,0:44:08.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 就像虛構的機車中的天才\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Yeah, like an imaginary genius in the engine.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.18,0:44:11.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或是梅蘭妮用完美的科學手段 來拯救我們\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Or Melanie saving us with perfect science.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.30,0:44:14.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或是為我們指路的幸存者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Or a survivor to show us the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.23,0:44:16.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- So...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.69,0:44:19.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我們繼續前進 -同意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we press on. - Agreed.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.06,0:44:21.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們還能怎樣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- What else are we gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.36,0:44:24.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喬西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Josie?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.82,0:44:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們最好是對的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Well, we better be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.37,0:44:39.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位乘客同伴們 我們偉大的征程將繼續\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Fellow passengers, our great endeavor continues.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.79,0:44:46.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們已表態 根據少數服從多數原則 我們將前往新伊甸園\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You have spoken, and by majority rule, we are heading for New Eden.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.24,0:45:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,字幕翻譯：黛拉

